parameters:
Cerburus Octopus: Looks like the advertising paid off! We've
definitely got more customers now!!

Memimi: Acting all high and mighty... Just because you won
once by a fluke... ugh...

Memimi: (...Anyway, I'm grateful I could wear proper
clothes... The new boss is detestable, but that's none of
the customers' concern. I must remain professional in my
service...)

Cerburus Octopus: While you were out promoting, I added a
new star product! Plus, from now on, we'll be running a free
campaign for all customers who enter!!

Cerburus Octopus: Look, this is the new product... learn
about it quickly!!

Memimi: Don't yell, it's so loud... umm... is this a DVD or
something...?

Memimi: ...What!!? Th-this... th-th-th-th-this... ah...!
My... ah-ahhh!!?

Cerburus Octopus: It's your secret erotic videos that I've
been filming on the sly!! Since Shark Broccoli is just a
lowly member of our organization... we own the rights to his
image!

Memimi: (What... what!? Wait a minute... this is clearly
showing stuff that shouldn't be uncensored... and my real
name, face, school name, and even where I work are all
written clearly...? Selling this...?)
Memimi: How much is this for...

Cerburus Octopus: Stop dawdling! We have customers waiting!!
You've got to handle the free campaign too!

Cerburus Octopus: Every customer who visits will receive a
welcome blowjob from our part-timer, Shark Mountain Memimi-
chan! No other convenience store gives out such a service
for free... it's revolutionary!!

Memimi: Ew... blowjob, wha-what...!? Hey wait! Wait wait
wait wait wait... what are you doing without my consent!?

Cerburus Octopus: You don't like the manager's strategy?
Surely the city's strongest S-class monster, Shark Broccoli
himself, isn't scared of giving blowjobs, right?

Memimi: (No no... this is just impossible... it's crazy!
Even if I am the city's strongest monster, giving blowjobs
to an unspecified number of people... is obviously
disgusting! I should refuse... this is a situation I can
escape from...!)

Memimi: Gah... ha... I have no problem with blowjobs or
videos... Scared? Ha, as if I'd be scared of sucking on some
soggy pork bits from the masses...

Memimi: Well, I certainly don't like your vulgar strategies!
You should consider what it's like for me, having to deal
with the impoverished ideas of a lowly manager! Ridiculous,
just line up the customers already!

Cerburus Octopus: Grrr... always acting so superior... Oh,
you'll see how effective my management strategy is from the
best seat in the house...!

Memimi: (I-I said it againnnnnn...! More unnecessary
bravado... there's no taking it back now...! What do I do...
really do it with my mouth...? All of the customers'...?
Uwaaaaaaah...)
